OL,3,C'Horrendous' scenes within NI
OL,4,Cemergency departments
OL,6,FDoctors, nurses and unions have
OL,7,Fdescribed scenes inside Northern
OL,8,FIreland's hospital emergency
OL,9,Fdepartments as "horrendous", with
OL,10,Fpatients on floors, overcrowded
OL,11,Fcubicles and long waits for admission
OL,12,Fand treatment.
OL,14,FIt comes as the health service remains
OL,15,Funder significant pressure, with the
OL,16,FHealth Department saying high levels
OL,17,Fof flu cases are "a significant
OL,18,Fcontributory factor".
