OL,3,C'Horrendous' scenes within NI
OL,4,Cemergency departments
OL,6,FRita Devlin from the Royal College of
OL,7,FNursing painted a picture of what it
OL,8,Fwas like in the ED at the Royal
OL,9,FVictoria Hospital on Friday afternoon.
OL,11,F"They're sitting in the back of
OL,12,Fambulances, in corridors, there was a
OL,13,Flady who had been sitting about five
OL,14,Fhours on a hard plastic chair," she
OL,15,Ftold UTV.
OL,17,F"We have older people people becoming
OL,18,Fbadly confused because of the
OL,19,Fenvironment, the noise, the light the
OL,20,Flack of sleep and obviously that's
OL,21,Fvery distressing for their families.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
