OL,3,C'Horrendous' scenes within NI
OL,4,Cemergency departments
OL,6,F"It is horrendous, it is a horrendous
OL,7,Fpicture and I don't think anyone would
OL,8,Fbelieve it until they've seen it
OL,9,Fthemselves.
OL,11,F"It feels immoral that we're asking
OL,12,Four nurses to go in day after day and
OL,13,Fdeal with the same issues, trying to
OL,14,Fdo the best they can, and they are
OL,15,Fabsolutely heartbroken at the care
OL,16,Fthat is being delivered to patients."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
