OL,3,C'Horrendous' scenes within NI
OL,4,Cemergency departments
OL,6,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt said the
OL,7,Fdepartment is looking to see if there
OL,8,Fare any "any unused levers" it can
OL,9,Fpull to try and alleviate some of the
OL,10,Fpressures.
OL,12,F"We talk about winter pressures but
OL,13,Factually that's almost an obsolete
OL,14,Fexpression, because these pressures
OL,15,Fare on emergency departments are 365
OL,16,Fdays a year," he told UTV.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
