OL,3,C'Horrendous' scenes within NI
OL,4,Cemergency departments
OL,6,F"But it is true that at this time of
OL,7,Fyear are additional pressures because
OL,8,Fof things like flu - this year
OL,9,Finfluenza is hitting an extraordinary
OL,10,Fnumber of people, not just in Northern
OL,11,FIreland but right across the UK and
OL,12,Fbeyond - and that's putting really
OL,13,Fextreme pressure on staff in ED.
OL,15,F"I want to thank the staff for all
OL,16,Fthey've done, their professionalism
OL,17,Fand empathy, and I also sympathise
OL,18,Fwith patients who are waiting too long
OL,19,Fto be seen."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
