OL,4,Cemergency departments
OL,6,FThe minister continued: "Winter
OL,7,Fpressures I think have been accepted
OL,8,Fby some, it's not going to be accepted
OL,9,Fby me.
OL,11,F"Yesterday I had a meeting with the
OL,12,FRCN, the Royal College of Emergency
OL,13,FMedicine, the Public Health Agency and
OL,14,Frepresentatives from one of the trusts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
