OL,3,C'Horrendous' scenes within NI
OL,4,Cemergency departments
OL,6,F"As well as looking for those
OL,7,Fadditional levers for this crisis, I
OL,8,Fwas saying once we get through this
OL,9,Fperiod, in late February or early
OL,10,FMarch, I want to sit down with all of
OL,11,Fthem with a blank page to make sure
OL,12,Fthat this time next year we're not
OL,13,Fgoing through the same old, same old."
